            ],
            "stanza_text": "Satan, criant miséricorde,\nAppela d'abord au secours\nEn voyant s'augmenter la horde\nQui, grâce à nous, chez lui déborde,\nSi bien que ses grils sont trop courts !\nEnsuite, il nous fit ce discours :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Faut-il donc que je vous proscrive,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Mortels que jadis j'attrapais !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "C'est effrayant ce qu'il m'arrive",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "De gens sur l'infernale rive,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Tassés, pressés en rangs épais,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Depuis que vous êtes en paix !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Faut-il donc que je vous proscrive,\nMortels que jadis j'attrapais !\nC'est effrayant ce qu'il m'arrive\nDe gens sur l'infernale rive,\nTassés, pressés en rangs épais,\nDepuis que vous êtes en paix !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Vous le savez, comme j'imite",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Les fables des temps primitifs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Les damnés, — on connaît ce mythe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Cuisent chez moi, dans la marmite",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Que j'ai prise dans les motifs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Des vieux poëtes inventifs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vous le savez, comme j'imite\nLes fables des temps primitifs,\nLes damnés, — on connaît ce mythe,\nCuisent chez moi, dans la marmite\nQue j'ai prise dans les motifs\nDes vieux poëtes inventifs."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Et, lorsque de rire je pouffe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Malheur à qui touche à ce pot !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Mais, — voici le comique bouffe !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Dans mon pot-au-feu l'on étouffe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Depuis que votre chassepot",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "A fait l'ancien fusil capot !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et, lorsque de rire je pouffe,\nMalheur à qui touche à ce pot !\nMais, — voici le comique bouffe !\nDans mon pot-au-feu l'on étouffe\nDepuis que votre chassepot\nA fait l'ancien fusil capot !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "On n'y peut plus tenir à l'aise,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Depuis que vos engins hideux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Fusils Bonnin et fusils Dreyse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Font rouler jusqu'à ma fournaise",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Un tas de passants hasardeux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Qui tombent là, coupés en deux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "On n'y peut plus tenir à l'aise,\nDepuis que vos engins hideux,\nFusils Bonnin et fusils Dreyse,\nFont rouler jusqu'à ma fournaise\nUn tas de passants hasardeux,\nQui tombent là, coupés en deux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Grâce enfin pour ma casserole !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Chacun de vous est le Colomb",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "D'une nouvelle arme à virole ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Vous vous foudroyez au pétrole",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Avec infiniment d'aplomb :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "C'est une débauche de plomb !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Grâce enfin pour ma casserole !\nChacun de vous est le Colomb\nD'une nouvelle arme à virole ;\nVous vous foudroyez au pétrole\nAvec infiniment d'aplomb :\nC'est une débauche de plomb !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Eh ! quoi, Dumanets sans vergogne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Croyez-vous que nous ricanons,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Quand là-haut votre clairon grogne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "En voyant la folle besogne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Que me préparent vos canons,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Dont je ne retiens pas les noms !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Eh ! quoi, Dumanets sans vergogne,\nCroyez-vous que nous ricanons,\nQuand là-haut votre clairon grogne,\nEn voyant la folle besogne\nQue me préparent vos canons,\nDont je ne retiens pas les noms !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "On prétend que j'emmagasine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Tout ce que détruira le fer !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Dis, si tu veux, que je lésine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Tas de fous ! mais, dans ma cuisine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Où flambe un feu joyeux et clair,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Je n'ai plus de place en enfer !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "On prétend que j'emmagasine\nTout ce que détruira le fer !\nDis, si tu veux, que je lésine,\nTas de fous ! mais, dans ma cuisine\nOù flambe un feu joyeux et clair,\nJe n'ai plus de place en enfer !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "J'étais gai comme Diogène ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "J'engraissais comme un alderman !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Vais-je, pour qu'on me morigène,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Exproprier ce qui me gêne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Comme votre baron Haussmann,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Moi bon vivant et gentleman !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J'étais gai comme Diogène ;\nJ'engraissais comme un alderman !\nVais-je, pour qu'on me morigène,\nExproprier ce qui me gêne,\nComme votre baron Haussmann,\nMoi bon vivant et gentleman !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! tu t'égorges, saltimbanque,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Genre humain encore au maillot !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Toujours des morts ! — La place manque ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "S'il en vient un, je vous le flanque",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "(Fût-il juif, turc ou parpaillot)",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Dans le paradis de Veuillot !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ah ! tu t'égorges, saltimbanque,\nGenre humain encore au maillot !\nToujours des morts ! — La place manque ;\nS'il en vient un, je vous le flanque\n(Fût-il juif, turc ou parpaillot)\nDans le paradis de Veuillot !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Là, vêtu d'une simple écharpe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'à l'éternité sans fin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Ainsi qu'au concert Contrescarpe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Il entendra des airs de harpe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Grattés par ce doux Séraphin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Et s'il s'amuse, il sera fin !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Là, vêtu d'une simple écharpe,\nJusqu'à l'éternité sans fin,\nAinsi qu'au concert Contrescarpe,\nIl entendra des airs de harpe\nGrattés par ce doux Séraphin,\nEt s'il s'amuse, il sera fin !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Mais, pauvre ver, pour deux aurores,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Vis tranquille sur ton mûrier !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Pourquoi faut-il que tu t'abhorres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Frêle insecte, et que tu dévores,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "En croyant mâcher du laurier,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Tout le plomb que vend l'armurier !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais, pauvre ver, pour deux aurores,\nVis tranquille sur ton mûrier !\nPourquoi faut-il que tu t'abhorres,\nFrêle insecte, et que tu dévores,\nEn croyant mâcher du laurier,\nTout le plomb que vend l'armurier !"
        }
